# Word Study Methodology

When creating or analyzing biblical word/symbol studies, you MUST follow this process.

## CRITICAL: Show Your Work

**You MUST explicitly show your work at every step.** Do NOT do "mental math" or keep analysis in your head. Write out:
- Every search you perform and its results
- Every verse you examine
- Every candidate meaning you consider
- Every substitution test with explicit before/after

